<!-----------------About company-------------------->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <img src="img/about1.jpg" class="img-thumbnail" style="border-radius:250px 0px 250px 250px">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="well">
                    <h3>Who We Are</h3>
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        Afza Slaughter House (ASH) was established in 2017. From its very inception, ASH has had one singular
                        focus-its functioning be devoted to Islamic law and dedicated to the following the guidelines of the
                        <span style="color:darkred">Holy Qur'an.</span>
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        The company commenced as a specialty farming business involved in growing and producing Halal poultry
                        products for Toronto, the Greater Toronto Area and Ottawa. ASH soon ventured into other meat products
                        and flourished over the years as one of the leading halal slaughter houses in Canada.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
